22
00:02:08,693 --> 00:02:09,819
Tem vergonha na cara, cabrão.

23
00:02:10,695 --> 00:02:12,488
Estás a ajudar os infiéis.

24
00:02:12,572 --> 00:02:14,949
Podes desligar o camião e sair?

25
00:02:15,033 --> 00:02:16,784
Obriga-me.

26
00:02:16,868 --> 00:02:18,244
Há aqui algum problema?

27
00:02:23,374 --> 00:02:25,126
KAWA MAWLAYEE
PRIMEIRO-SARGENTO

28
00:02:25,209 --> 00:02:27,295
Eddie? O Chow Chow?

29
00:02:27,545 --> 00:02:28,588
{\an8}EDUARDO "CHOW CHOW" LOPEZ
PRIMEIRO-SARGENTO

30
00:02:28,671 --> 00:02:30,798
{\an8}O Eddie já acabou. Tom?

31
00:02:31,257 --> 00:02:32,842
Não fales comigo. Fala com o John.

32
00:02:32,925 --> 00:02:34,052
TOM "TOM CAT" HANCOCK
SARGENTO

33
00:02:35,595 --> 00:02:36,888
John! O Chow Chow?

34
00:02:38,056 --> 00:02:39,682
O que tem aqui atrás?

35
00:02:40,058 --> 00:02:40,933
Jack Jack?

36
00:02:41,517 --> 00:02:42,935
É estranho, John!

37
00:02:43,352 --> 00:02:45,104
Espera. Vou aí ter.

38
00:02:46,981 --> 00:02:50,610
{\an8}JOHN KINLEY
SARGENTO-CHEFE

39
00:02:53,237 --> 00:02:54,363
Manda-o abrir.

40
00:02:55,698 --> 00:02:56,866
